<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error - Trading.tf</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif; 
            background: #1b2838; 
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .error-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 4rem auto;
            background: #2a475e;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ff4444;
        }
        h1 { color: #ff4444; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .btn { 
            background: #66c0f4; 
            color: #1b2838; 
            padding: 10px 20px; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            border-radius: 4px; 
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <h1>⚠️ <%= message %></h1>
        <p>We encountered an error while processing your request.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn">Return to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>